                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Related question: &lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/q/28400690/2142994&quot;&gt;Python3 correct way to import relative or absolute?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/2142994/ani-menon&quot; title=&quot;25,460 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Ani Menon&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
